attributes.action: Make Muswell Hill Independant of Haringey Council
attributes.additional_details:
Make Muswell Hill Independant of Haringey Council.

Muswell Hill area is economically socially and politically divorced from other parts of Haringey Coucil controlled areas of North London.

Haringey Council is well known or infamous for being:
1. One of the worst run councils in UK
2. One of the most profligate spending councils in UK
3. One of the highest council taxes in UK
4. One of the worst customer services in UK
